@page "/components/HxTooltip"

<h1>@nameof(HxTooltip)</h1>
<p class="lead">
	Bootstrap Tooltip. Rendered as a span (see example in <a href="https://getbootstrap.com/docs/5.0/components/tooltips/#disabled-elements">Disabled elements</a> in the Bootstrap tooltip documentation).
	<a href="https://getbootstrap.com/docs/5.0/components/tooltips/">https://getbootstrap.com/docs/5.0/components/tooltips/</a>
</p>

<p>The tooltips actives on hover only.</p>

<h3>Properties</h3>
<ul>
	<li>
		<strong>@nameof(HxTooltip.Text)</strong><br />
		Tooltip text.
	</li>
	<li>
		<strong>@nameof(HxTooltip.Placement)</strong><br />
		Tooltip placement (position).
	</li>
</ul>

<h3>@nameof(HxButton) support</h3>
The tooltip support is also embedded in @nameof(HxButton).

